#~ msgid ""
#~ "Also, you will have to select the puzzle type. &palapeli; does not "
#~ "restrict you to classic puzzle pieces, other puzzle types can be easily "
#~ "added by third-party developers. Each puzzle type may offer a set of "
#~ "further properties, such as the piece count."
